EXPECT_IN_CONTAINS_NEXT "\"method\":\"session/prompt\""
OUT {"jsonrpc":"2.0","id":3,"result":{}}
OUT {"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"session/update","params":{"sessionId":"947e5b6c-12bb-4564-83e3-664ac1d1b60c","update":{"sessionUpdate":"agent_thought_chunk","content":{"type":"text","text":"**Inventing Distinctive Codenames**\n\nI'm currently exploring creative codenames for our session. My focus is on brevity and distinctiveness, aiming for something memorable and relevant to our current interaction. I'm aiming for a four-word or fewer explanation.\n\n"}}}}
OUT {"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"session/update","params":{"sessionId":"947e5b6c-12bb-4564-83e3-664ac1d1b60c","update":{"sessionUpdate":"agent_thought_chunk","content":{"type":"text","text":"**Crafting Memorable Handles**\n\nI'm currently focused on devising a unique identifier for our ongoing dialogue. The aim is to select something concise yet striking, capturing the essence of our interaction. My goal is a four-word or less descriptor.\n\n"}}}}
OUT {"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"session/update","params":{"sessionId":"947e5b6c-12bb-4564-83e3-664ac1d1b60c","update":{"sessionUpdate":"agent_thought_chunk","content":{"type":"text","text":"**Devising Unique Chat Identifiers**\n\nI'm currently focused on conceptualizing a distinctive moniker for our interaction, aiming for something concise and evocative that encapsulates the nature of our dialogue. My objective is to find a fitting title that is four words or less.\n\n"}}}}
OUT {"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"session/update","params":{"sessionId":"947e5b6c-12bb-4564-83e3-664ac1d1b60c","update":{"sessionUpdate":"agent_thought_chunk","content":{"type":"text","text":"**Formulating Codewords**\n\nI am currently focused on generating a unique designation for our ongoing exchange. My priority is a concise and evocative moniker that captures the essence of our interaction, aiming for a descriptor of four words or less.\n\n"}}}}
OUT {"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"session/update","params":{"sessionId":"947e5b6c-12bb-4564-83e3-664ac1d1b60c","update":{"sessionUpdate":"agent_message_chunk","content":{"type":"text","text":"Syntax Sentinel: Guards code syntax."}}}}
